snippet.textDisplay:
As a huge skeptic of new shows, especially ones so closely related to previous iterations, I'm a tough sell.
WOW. This show is DAMN good.
Sure, it's a great premise we all know and love, done with high level cameras and editing, with 3 distinct personalities that work together.
What i find truly special is the manner in which it came about: Bringing together 3 different youtube channels all grown separately, with their own fanbases grown and matured over the last couple/few years independently.....AND IT WORKS! So often its attempted and falls flat, but this super group is awesome.
